item.title: Back Brace Body Jacket
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
Intended for folks with arthritis or instability of the lumbar spine. The additional support offers relief to lower back pain while limiting flexion, stretching, and bending. Assists in recovery with spondylolysis, herniated or bulging disc, lumbar fracture management, post-operative stabilization, and spinal stenosis.

The post Back Brace Body Jacket appeared first on AT Surgical.
item.content:encoded:
• Full support for thoracic to lumbar region
  • Main Velcro® closure with three additional belts for optimal adjustment
  • Special poly insert for firm support
  • Keystone pad gives extra lumbar support

item.title: Erectus LSO Back Support Brace
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
Are you suffering from lower back pain? The Erectus provides coverage from the sacral spine to the L5 vertebra, granting improved spinal stabilization and reduced strain. Equipped with rigid anterior & posterior removable panels. The mechanical advantage system utilizes bi-lateral tension straps, allowing a 6:1 pull ratio & giving positive patient compliance.

  • Reduces strain on discs
  • Diverts weight bearing forces to the lumbar spine area
  • Manages pain for improved quality of life

item.title: Pure Gel Corn Protector Rings
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
The Fresco Pure Gel Corn Protector Ring is a toe ring made of very soft elastic Deramed® Gel specially designed to protect the dorsal region of the toes. It is specially designed with a thick top and a gap for the corn ensures perfect positioning to protect painful corns. Instantly relieves pain and discomfort. Prevents the appearance of new corns, especially in the case of claw or hammer toes.

The post Pure Gel Corn Protector Rings appeared first on AT Surgical.
item.content:encoded:
• Offers protection for the dorsal region of the toes and helps to minimize the appearance of new corns
  • Made of soft and elastic Deramed® gel that contains mineral oil to moisturize and hydrate the skin, helping to break down calluses
  • Designed with a thick top and gap to ensure maximum comfort for the wearer by minimizing contact with and eliminating pressure on the corn
  • Durable, washable and reusable
  • Sold in pairs

The post Pure Gel Corn Protector Rings appeared first on AT Surgical.

item.title: Pure Gel Self Adhesive Comfort Spur Heel Cups
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
Fresco Pure Gel Self Adhesive Comfort Spur Heel Cups absorb shock to help relieve and prevent heel pain. This heel cup is made from medical grade silicone and is hypoallergenic. It offers comfort, cushioning, and maximum shock absorption for relief from heel spurs, plantar fasciitis, foot, ankle, knee and back pain.

The post Pure Gel Self Adhesive Comfort Spur Heel Cups appeared first on AT Surgical.
item.content:encoded:
Help protect the calcaneus and all associated skeletal structures (knees, hips, and spinal column) from the destructive forces of shock. The large, soft and center posting provide additional cushioning and take pressure off painful areas. Can be washed in hot or cold water, using any kind of soap or detergent and can be dried at temperatures of up to 500º C. There is no need for talcum powder

  • Breathable, hypoallergenic
  • Low profile design – use in dress shoes or athletic shoes
  • Comes as a pair fitting left and right
  • Pads and absorbs shock to protect sore heels or heel spurs from direct pressure
  • Wedge shaped footplate keeps the foot in dorsi-flexed position to help maintain correct posture while gently stretching the tendons
  • Hypoallergenic self adhesive backing securely fastenes the heel cups in place
  • Made from 100% medical grade silicone
  • Latex Free

The post Pure Gel Self Adhesive Comfort Spur Heel Cups appeared first on AT Surgical.

item.title: Mesh Lumbar Sacro LSO Back Brace
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
The 592 Series Mesh Back Brace with or without Tension Straps and an optional Sacro Pad is a great solution for those seeking a premium LSO (Lumbo-Sacral) Support. This brace features a cool, breathable mesh back panel and two aluminum stays for stability.

The post Mesh Lumbar Sacro LSO Back Brace appeared first on AT Surgical.
item.content:encoded:
• Model 592 features the brace only without tension straps or sacro pad.
  • Model 593 features two adjustable elastic tension straps for a comfortable fit but excludes the sacro pad.
  • Model 594 includes the elastic tension straps and comes with a sacro pad for additional sacro lumbar support.
